Package: clvotes
Type: Package
Title: An R package for downloading data from the Commons and Lords Votes API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Noel",
        family = "Dempsey",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "noel.dempsey@outlook.com") 
Description: This package provides a collection of functions for downloading
    data from the different endpoints of the UK Parliament's Commons and Lords 
    Votes API. The core functions offer simple way to send queries to the API
    endpoints and receive the results as a tibble with data converted to the
    approriate R data type.
